General.Name: Dis-Chem Pharmacies
General.Description: Dis-Chem Pharmacies Limited, together with its subsidiaries, engages in the retail and wholesale of pharmaceuticals in South Africa. The company operates through two segments, Retail and Wholesale. It owns and operates a chain of retail stores that offers a range of products, including dispensary, personal care and beauty, healthcare and nutrition, baby care, and other products; and offers ancillary services such as clinics, and hair and beauty salons. The company also manages an online platform that provides click & collect services. In addition, it is involved in the wholesale of pharmaceutical and health products; and provision of customer loyalty programs. The company was founded in 1978 and is headquartered in Midrand, South Africa.
